---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Me"
  description="I am a software engineer passionate about scalable systems."
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl sm:text-[2.75rem] font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 font-sans"
    >
      About Me
    </h1>
    <p>Hi There &#128075;&#127995;,</p>
    <p>
      I'm Savitha, a software developer based in India who loves to explore new
      technologies, <a
        href="https://github.com/g-savitha"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover">build projects</a
      >, and share my knowledge with others. While I've worked with many
      programming languages, I'm particularly enthusiastic about JavaScript and
      its ecosystem &#10084;&#65039;.
    </p>
    <p>
      My preferred tech stack includes <strong
        >Node.js, Typescript, React, Styled Components, Mongo/Postgres, and Jest</strong
      >. When I'm not coding, I enjoy playing video games and chess. I'm also an
      avid reader of non-fiction and a music enthusiast. In my free time, I love
      to capture the world through my camera lens. Additionally, I enjoy reading
      books on philosophy and Indian mythology.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm always up for discussing and exchanging ideas with others who share my
      interests. If any of the above fascinates you, or if you have any
      opportunities, open-source ideas, or need any assistance, feel free to
      reach out to me via <a
        href="mailto:gsavitha@protonmail.com?subject=Hello"
        class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover">email</a
      > or X <a
        href="https://x.com/gsavitha_"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover">@gsavitha_</a
      >. If you prefer LinkedIn, you can always send me a connection request.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
